Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.65,0:00:05.31,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right, Kanie had a crush on Natori back then, didn't he?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.35,0:00:09.78,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,W-What did he just say?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.61,0:00:14.54,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Let's go do karaoke!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.39,0:00:17.86,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kanie felt that way about me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.35,0:00:19.78,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That can't be true.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.11,0:00:22.01,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Hey, Miyoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.01,0:00:23.50,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.99,0:00:25.26,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Are you still half-asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.39,0:00:28.73,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}W-What's going on?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.73,0:00:30.50,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why is he staring at me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.89,0:00:33.93,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Skirt length, makeup, hair...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.93,0:00:35.14,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,...all against code.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.49,0:00:36.25,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.25,0:00:39.51,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, I see. This must be a dress code inspection.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.03,0:00:43.22,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Come to the sociology prep room during your lunch break.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.77,0:00:44.52,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.52,0:00:45.58,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.55,0:00:49.66,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Seriously, what was I even thinking...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.52,0:00:55.52,Signs,,0,0,0,,The 25 Year Old High School Girl
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.52,0:00:55.52,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(27.333,675)}Episode 5: How Could I Have Lost Those?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.93,0:01:02.04,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I've been thinking about this since that first day...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.14,0:01:02.04,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,0)}Sociology Prep Room
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.37,0:01:04.14,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,What's with that getup?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.67,0:01:10.38,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,And your makeup—you were hardly wearing any at the class reunion.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.73,0:01:14.29,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,T-That's because Kaho is a really showy girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.29,0:01:17.05,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I-I don't like it any more than you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.79,0:01:22.15,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,And here I thought you just liked dressing up that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.15,0:01:24.16,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,A-As if!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.29,0:01:28.98,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,But as your teacher, I need to discipline you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.31,0:01:31.50,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Wha—Kanie!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.61,0:01:35.32,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Are you going to disobey a teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.07,0:01:50.85,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Huh? W-What are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.85,0:01:51.88,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.49,0:01:56.76,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,You're light as a feather.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.22,0:02:00.36,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,W-Wait, you can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.89,0:02:02.05,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Behave, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.13,0:02:05.78,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.58,0:02:25.12,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,W-Wait, don't just...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.81,0:02:27.46,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Why? You don't need them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.41,0:02:43.39,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}That reminds me, don't we have a test coming up?{\i0}{I can't hear the word in the middle of this sentance, so this may or may not be right}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.39,0:02:43.84,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Oh, yeah.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.84,0:02:46.71,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,No, Kanie! I mean it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.71,0:02:48.39,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,A-At this rate, we'll be...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.27,0:02:52.36,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,You're right. It's just like last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.40,0:02:56.35,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Oh, shit, I didn't do my homework!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.35,0:02:57.40,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.71,0:03:01.12,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,No, this might be worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.77,0:03:04.30,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,There's no telling when someone will come in, or who it will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.67,0:03:06.14,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.23,0:03:10.36,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Shall we give them something even better to look at?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.35,0:03:16.32,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}N-No, you can't! I'm begging you, Kanie... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.63,0:03:20.33,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Stop, please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.33,0:03:22.58,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,There's the bell. I guess that's as far as we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.35,0:03:23.64,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.39,0:03:27.34,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Oh, are you saying you wish we could have kept going?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.23,0:03:30.14,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,O-Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.79,0:03:35.51,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I-I have to get back to class.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.51,0:03:37.33,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Don't trip over yourself getting there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.33,0:03:39.19,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I'll be perfectly fine, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.87,0:03:43.20,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Huh? Why is it locked?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.55,0:03:47.70,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,There's no way I'd do that without locking the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.71,0:03:53.21,Signs,,0,0,0,,Sociology Prep Room
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.21,0:03:55.21,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I-If you'll excuse me, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.39,0:03:59.88,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I'll never get tired of watching her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.29,0:04:01.72,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.33,0:04:02.98,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.25,0:04:10.22,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damnit, I just {\i0}know{\i1} Kanie is enjoying himself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.89,0:04:12.48,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.21,0:04:15.74,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,My butt feels kind of cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.81,0:04:19.40,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I-I forgot my panties!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.53,0:04:22.12,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Oh, hey Kaho.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.79,0:04:27.74,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,What's the matter? Class is about to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.29,0:04:33.36,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,W-W-What do I do now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.47,0:04:34.03,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}Who could have predicted this reunion?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.03,0:04:35.02,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,705)}I reel in this thread of memory, and use it to spin my tale
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.94,0:04:42.08,Songs,,0,0,0,,I reel in this thread of memory, and use it to spin my tale
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.08,0:04:46.96,Songs,,0,0,0,,Why are you all pushy one minute,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.96,0:04:52.72,Songs,,0,0,0,,and then gentle the next?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.07,0:04:58.22,Songs,,0,0,0,,As long as the two of us share this secret
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.22,0:05:03.78,Songs,,0,0,0,,it will be the light that guides you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.78,0:05:08.56,Songs,,0,0,0,,to somewhere in the yet-unknowable future
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.56,0:05:13.00,Songs,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you, it's okay to optimistic
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.00,0:05:17.04,Songs,,0,0,0,,I want to know everything about you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.04,0:05:22.48,Songs,,0,0,0,,hidden deep within those eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.48,0:05:27.74,Songs,,0,0,0,,I can't control these feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.74,0:05:34.90,Songs,,0,0,0,,Piece by piece, my heart is being snatched away
